{
  "stem": "268.6",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I, I really don't play that well.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I, I-- [LAUGHS] not, not to pick up-- not picking on Schubert, but-- [LAUGHS] he was a great composer, wrote a lot of Romantic music.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I, I really don't do that piece.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Of course, on an occasion like this, when we-- when we bringing back memories, it's, it's, it's really befitting that I do play that piece.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that, that single piece is responsible for my survival.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I must have played a whole lot better then, but-- at least that piece.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I, I enjoy playing liturgical music, some jazz and some popular.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But that was the incident in there for-- that saved my life.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Thank you for playing that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I said, thank you for playing it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, you're welcome.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- there's more to that movement.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I, I should be actually in two-- in two verses, which I-- which I did then, actually, in three, or so.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But it takes a lot of technique and, and practicing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "However, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] from that, we, we, we moved on.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That camp was liquidated again.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And, and I pulled through until perhaps '44.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "By December, it's already '44.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "May or June, they-- and they shipped us to another camp.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The name of that camp was Funfteichen.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Literally translated, it means-- 'funf' means five; 'Teichen' is ponds-- the, the 'Five Lakes,' Five Lakes Town.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That camp was a huge camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The factories there-- we were working in factories-- one of them was Krupp, K-R-U-P-P, munitions factories, engines.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And again, the same routine, except it was a larger camp and a lot of Polish population.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I found myself-- my, my Polish conversations and my-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] better-than-average Polish language.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
